poem-zj0ojo7VNPsd4cI28vFS9w">Kỳ 6 - 其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/T%C3%A2y-giao-l%E1%BA%A1c-hoa-ca/poem-jyO0RzeP5_bTHpqrU9OhkQ">Tây giao lạc hoa ca - 西郊落花歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cung-T%E1%BB%B1-Tr%C3%A2n/author-7r72VrPQwdDMRtQY4fV6gg">Cung Tự Trân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%A0-ph%E1%BB%A7-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-lai-kinh/poem-3pg9heB3b-2GocIRMk-9ww">Tiễn Hà phủ Phạm đại nhân lai kinh - 餞河撫範大人來京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3mvgQ8jqLVNdE0oNQACUCg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 2 - 詠懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
